            . I am a <rs id="t18310217-125-viclabel741" type="occupation">carrier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-125-victim1291 t18310217-125-viclabel741"></join>, and live in Great Dover-street. On the 17th of February I was in Longlane, near the pig-market at <placeName id="t18310217-125-crimeloc742">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310217-125-crimeloc742" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310217-125-crimeloc742" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-125-off739 t18310217-125-crimeloc742"></join>, and felt a twitch at my coat pocket; I turned, and saw the prisoner about a yard from me - he was the nearest person to me: I seized him instantly, and observed him shifting his coat -I suspected he had my handkerchief; I put my hand into his breast pocket, and pulled it out - this is it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310217-125-person1293">
                  THOMAS 
                  BARKER
               <interp inst="t18310217-125-person1293" type="surname" value="BARKER"></interp>
