                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and produce the handkerchief, which I received from the witness, with the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not do it - there were two lads who threw it down; I picked it up, and put it into my pocket - the other two ran away.</p>
               <p>MR. HOPKINS. There were no lads near me.</p>
